HTML :
<div class="slider"> → Container for images
<img> → Image elements inside the slider
<button class="prev"> and <button class="next"> → Navigation buttons

CSS :
overflow: hidden; → Hides overflowing images
display: flex; → Aligns images in a row
transition: transform 0.5s ease-in-out; → Creates smooth sliding animation

JavaScript :
querySelectorAll(".slider img") → Selects all images
addEventListener("click", function) → Detects button clicks
setInterval() → Automatically changes images at intervals
style.transform = "translateX()" → Moves images left/right
